---
// PrivacyFirst.astro
---
<section class="mb-8 p-6 rounded-xl bg-canvas border border-hairline shadow-sm relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="relative z-10">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
      <div class="p-2 bg-success/10 rounded-full">
        <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-success" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight text-ink">Privacy First Guarantee</h2>
    </div>
    
    <p class="text-sm text-body leading-relaxed">
      Unlike most online image tools that upload your private photos to remote servers for processing, our tools operate <strong class="text-ink">100% locally in your web browser</strong>. We utilize modern WebAssembly and the HTML5 Canvas API to perform all conversions, optimizations, and edits directly on your device.
    </p>
    
    <div class="mt-5 space-y-2">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-mono text-mute uppercase tracking-widest bg-canvas-soft px-3 py-2 rounded border border-hairline">
        <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-success"></span>
        Zero Server Uploads
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-mono text-mute uppercase tracking-widest bg-canvas-soft px-3 py-2 rounded border border-hairline">
        <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-success"></span>
        No Data Collection
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-mono text-mute uppercase tracking-widest bg-canvas-soft px-3 py-2 rounded border border-hairline">
        <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-success"></span>
        Instant Deletion
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
